          </div>
          <div class="service-info">
            <h2>Workshops & Seminars</h2>
            <p>Al Iman Foundation regularly organizes educational workshops and seminars on various topics to enhance students' knowledge and skills. These events feature expert speakers and interactive sessions.</p>
            <h3>Upcoming Events</h3>
            <ul class="event-list">
              <li>
                <div class="event-date">
                  <span class="day">15</span>
                  <span class="month">May</span>
                </div>
